{"tid":1459111,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港交所對香港 係一種咩存在價值？","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:36:54.000Z","uid":28106,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4406b4db3102aa0de2548027d0ba730d03d6fc","tid":1459111,"uid":28106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"就咁 見班黃絲開始識得向影響香港經濟同聲譽埋手<br />\n我想將我由6月果陣嘅愚見同大家分享下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">圍堵 港交所</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我讀書真係唔多 所以想問下大家<br />\n見新聞每日都報恒指幾多、股票升跌幅情況<br />\n咁相信股票市場對香港嘅經濟應該有一定程度嘅影響<br />\n<br />\n如果有人咁痴線走去搞我哋咁重要嘅港交所<br />\n香港會唔會冧架？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你班死黃絲真係唔好亂咁黎呀出事架嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由佢哋圍囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔准搞港交所"},{"pid":"16aab4b3152fdb13d74ea635580131738bda7ffb","tid":1459111,"uid":288675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"...港交所全部電子化<br />\n你去FB 可否令Facebook 不能運作？"},{"pid":"56b2d12d6c767d80c5cb4ef8e3eb317a8caccc2c","tid":1459111,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcM0VfH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcM0VfH.png&h=a5818d5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"390efcfe2129a7bf9b57406a13e098f6859b3247","tid":1459111,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"圍港交所 無撚用架<br />\n除非全香港停電"},{"pid":"c168b24591967123004709c5034f4fcc00ee31a5","tid":1459111,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"無用"},{"pid":"ce07a60b8cb4490c8bf57efad01067bb7b571cf0","tid":1459111,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"已經網上處理<br />\n變咗做博物館<br />\n圍佢冇意義"},{"pid":"6663c7623